{"tid":2320514,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國啟動撤銷中國電信在美營運許可 華為被正式列入威脅國家安全名單","createTime":"2020-12-11T01:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-14T07:21:28.000Z","uid":300625,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"c1926b771c355c57f701fdcf61834277bb205b75","tid":2320514,"uid":300625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:26:29.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦通信委員會(FCC)已啟動撤銷中國電信(<a href=\"http://00728.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00728.HK&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=28d7f9f4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00728.HK</a>)在美國營運的許可程序，FCC主席Ajit Pai表示，數個美國政府機構在出於國家安全的考慮下，建議FCC停止中國電信在美國的業務，因擔心中國電信會被迫遵守中國政府包括攔截通訊等要求。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.aastocks.com/share/news/aafn/NOW.1062472/?lang=Chi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Fshare%2Fnews%2Faafn%2FNOW.1062472%2F%3Flang%3DChi&d=%2B91LnCbTcEAXcT2WrppvqQESYyyjRTN6W0WnX97q4IQ%3D&h=bf154912\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.aastocks.com/share/news/aafn/NOW.1062472/?lang=Chi</a>"},{"pid":"e56f2f9a0e81157b7e4412e90fff70385d59031c","tid":2320514,"uid":300625,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:28:43.000Z","msg":"華為係咪可以正式收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d7e532c23efb1fd3279acbd5c5d7f2565e22cd0","tid":2320514,"uid":12599,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f7e623fd464978237ccea82d33cdbdb0a189c7f","tid":2320514,"uid":209248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:32:08.000Z","msg":"我以回國為國出力"},{"pid":"bd489d18845d284403752ab53c2bf6910b9121a9","tid":2320514,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-11T01:33:20.000Z","msg":"5G gg"